high_descs: Turn left and go to the table.
Pick up the apple on the table.
Go right and bring the apple to the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Bring the heated apple back to the table on the side.
Put the heated apple on the table in front of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn around, will forward, then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the apple from the table.
Turn right, move forward, turn left, then move forward and to approach the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave.
Turn right, move forward, turn right, move forward, then turn right into approach the table.
Place the apple on the table, in front of the pepper and to the right of the soap.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple on the table.

high_descs: Move to the table to the left of the door to the right of the stove.
Pick up an apple from the table.
Move to the microwave to the right of the door.
Heat the apple with the microwave before removing it and closing the door.
Move to the table to the right of the stove from before.
Place the apple on top of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple on the table by the stove.
